source.oracleReaderQuery:
WITH max_subacctnbr AS (
  SELECT TRANSACTIONID, MAX(SUBACCTNBR) AS MAX_SUBACCTNBR
  FROM DNACUSTOM.VW_DIGITALBANKINGTRANSACTIONS
  GROUP BY TRANSACTIONID
), max_count_subacctnbr AS (
  SELECT TRANSACTIONID, COUNT(*) AS COUNT_SUBACCTNBR
  FROM DNACUSTOM.VW_DIGITALBANKINGTRANSACTIONS
  GROUP BY TRANSACTIONID
  ORDER BY COUNT_SUBACCTNBR DESC
  FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY
)
SELECT t1.*
FROM DNACUSTOM.VW_DIGITALBANKINGTRANSACTIONS t1
JOIN max_subacctnbr t2 ON t1.TRANSACTIONID = t2.TRANSACTIONID AND t1.SUBACCTNBR = t2.MAX_SUBACCTNBR
JOIN max_count_subacctnbr t3 ON t1.TRANSACTIONID = t3.TRANSACTIONID;
